00:28:10,190 --> 00:28:11,350
Your notebooks.

579
00:28:16,710 --> 00:28:18,510
And some clothes to change with.

580
00:28:18,830 --> 00:28:20,490
There must be nothing inside.

581
00:28:22,150 --> 00:28:24,390
You haven't changed for so many days.

582
00:28:28,070 --> 00:28:29,480
Did they abuse you?

583
00:28:36,070 --> 00:28:36,790
Your…

584
00:28:40,830 --> 00:28:43,160
I forgot your model.

585
00:28:44,310 --> 00:28:45,630
I really forgot.

586
00:28:47,510 --> 00:28:48,230
Haimo,

587
00:28:49,190 --> 00:28:49,910
thank you.

588
00:28:53,790 --> 00:28:55,600
If I can get out this time…

589
00:28:57,430 --> 00:28:59,360
You will definitely be acquitted.

590
00:28:59,390 --> 00:29:01,030
I'll find the best lawyer

591
00:29:01,870 --> 00:29:04,110
and find all the witnesses at No. 90.

592
00:29:04,430 --> 00:29:05,470
Let the court

593
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:07,870
and all the people in Suzhou

594
00:29:08,470 --> 00:29:09,550
know

595
00:29:09,550 --> 00:29:11,080
what kind of person you are.

596
00:29:11,600 --> 00:29:14,260
Let them know what you've been doing these years

597
00:29:14,510 --> 00:29:16,910
and what difficulties we've been through.

598
00:29:17,110 --> 00:29:19,440
It was under Japanese occupation before,

599
00:29:19,710 --> 00:29:21,390
so we had no place to seek justice.

600
00:29:21,390 --> 00:29:23,590
But now we've won the War of Resistance.

601
00:29:23,830 --> 00:29:25,510
We are all Chinese.

602
00:29:25,550 --> 00:29:28,070
I don't believe there's still no way to seek justice.

603
00:29:28,070 --> 00:29:28,950
Nor do I believe

604
00:29:30,070 --> 00:29:31,390
that people like Zhou Zhifei

605
00:29:31,390 --> 00:29:32,920
won't be punished.

606
00:29:33,310 --> 00:29:34,440
As for this lawsuit,

607
00:29:34,510 --> 00:29:36,310
I will fight with them to the end!

608
00:29:36,670 --> 00:29:37,430
Yizhong.

609
00:29:39,510 --> 00:29:41,970
I will definitely make them clear your name.

610
00:29:53,230 --> 00:29:53,950
Thank you.

611
00:29:59,270 --> 00:30:02,550
[Shanghai News]

612
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:22,730
The last time there was such big snow in Suzhou

613
00:30:23,630 --> 00:30:25,830
was when I was in middle school.

614
00:30:29,440 --> 00:30:30,790
You leave the door and windows open.

615
00:30:30,790 --> 00:30:31,960
Aren't you cold?

616
00:30:33,230 --> 00:30:35,290
Your ears are red due to the coldness.

617
00:30:36,750 --> 00:30:39,270
The two new safes are about to be full.

618
00:30:40,190 --> 00:30:41,790
Should we buy two more?

619
00:30:43,620 --> 00:30:44,900
You decide.

620
00:30:44,950 --> 00:30:46,880
No need to ask me about everything!

621
00:30:49,330 --> 00:30:51,890
[The former director of the agent station of the Wang Regime; the current official for the reception of the NBIS]

622
00:30:53,020 --> 00:30:54,030
I was wondering…

623
00:30:54,910 --> 00:30:56,990
why you were angry all of a sudden.

624
00:30:59,150 --> 00:31:01,390
These tabloids just make up nonsense

625
00:31:01,410 --> 00:31:03,090
so that they can sell.

626
00:31:03,190 --> 00:31:04,950
Just ignore them.

627
00:31:06,000 --> 00:31:08,310
I really underestimated that Haimo.

628
00:31:08,590 --> 00:31:10,110
She jumped up and down.

629
00:31:10,190 --> 00:31:11,590
Do you know she went to Shanghai

630
00:31:11,590 --> 00:31:13,190
to find the famous lawyer Zhang Shizhao

631
00:31:13,190 --> 00:31:14,190
to take this case?

632
00:31:14,950 --> 00:31:16,250
Luckily, Zhang Shizhao

633
00:31:16,250 --> 00:31:19,650
is seeking to reverse the convition of Chu Minyi as a traitor.

634
00:31:19,750 --> 00:31:20,590
But still, he sent

635
00:31:20,590 --> 00:31:22,590
his right-hand assistant, Hu.

636
00:31:22,670 --> 00:31:24,350
We can't underestimate Hu, either.

637
00:31:24,350 --> 00:31:27,280
I'm afraid it's useless, no matter how capable he is.

638
00:31:27,360 --> 00:31:29,840
Gu Yizhong's name is on the list of traitors.

639
00:31:30,760 --> 00:31:32,620
Mr. Dai decided the case himself.

640
00:31:33,270 --> 00:31:35,800
Nothing is absolute.

641
00:31:36,150 --> 00:31:37,880
The Kuomintang Government now

642
00:31:37,910 --> 00:31:39,970
emphasizes the rule of law and public opinion.

643
00:31:39,970 --> 00:31:41,980
Chiang wants to win over the people.

644
00:31:42,430 --> 00:31:43,510
He doesn't shield

645
00:31:43,510 --> 00:31:45,770
those underground operatives anymore.

646
00:31:45,830 --> 00:31:46,830
Have you heard?

647
00:31:47,550 --> 00:31:48,440
Mr. Dai

648
00:31:48,710 --> 00:31:51,040
has placed Zhou Fohai under house arrest.

649
00:31:51,830 --> 00:31:53,310
Zhou may even be sued.

650
00:31:54,270 --> 00:31:56,830
We went underground earlier than Zhou Fohai.

651
00:31:57,150 --> 00:31:59,350
Our conviction was overturned in 1943.

652
00:32:00,150 --> 00:32:01,390
We also delivered

653
00:32:01,390 --> 00:32:03,520
so many important letters for Mr. Dai.

654
00:32:05,750 --> 00:32:07,310
I told you it was cold.

655
00:32:09,710 --> 00:32:11,100
If these newspapers

656
00:32:11,270 --> 00:32:12,630
don't have someone behind them,

657
00:32:12,630 --> 00:32:15,030
how did they dare to publish such nonsense?

658
00:32:15,790 --> 00:32:18,110
Clearly, someone is trying to overturn the case.

659
00:32:18,110 --> 00:32:19,310
It's really a pain.

660
00:32:21,550 --> 00:32:23,230
If Gu Yizhong tells everything

661
00:32:23,230 --> 00:32:25,070
that happened at No. 90 in court,

662
00:32:26,750 --> 00:32:28,410
it'll really make us look bad.

663
00:32:28,750 --> 00:32:29,110
No.

664
00:32:29,150 --> 00:32:30,880
I have to go to Shizikou Prison.

665
00:32:32,870 --> 00:32:34,200
Are you going there now?

666
00:32:34,710 --> 00:32:35,430
Didn't we agree

667
00:32:35,430 --> 00:32:37,030
we'll have Cangshu Mutton at home,

668
00:32:37,030 --> 00:32:39,430
and you'll have some high-grade Shaoxing wine with me tonight?

669
00:32:39,430 --> 00:32:42,030
Ren Yuandao's second concubine will come too.

670
00:32:42,930 --> 00:32:53,020
♫Holding the young emperor in your arms, you manage the country♫

671
00:32:51,750 --> 00:32:53,290
Alright, get up!

672
00:32:53,830 --> 00:32:55,430
You two, come out with me.

673
00:32:56,190 --> 00:32:58,150
What are you looking at? Hurry up!

674
00:32:58,480 --> 00:32:59,080
Get out!

675
00:33:00,750 --> 00:33:01,280
Hurry up!

676
00:33:09,190 --> 00:33:11,790
Yizhong, I'm here to visit you.

677
00:33:13,630 --> 00:33:14,340
How is it?

678
00:33:16,350 --> 00:33:17,790
This place is not bad.

679
00:33:19,670 --> 00:33:21,750
You've been locked up for almost half a year.

680
00:33:21,750 --> 00:33:24,410
And you're engaging in academic studies again.

681
00:33:24,550 --> 00:33:26,210
Academic studies is my field.

682
00:33:28,150 --> 00:33:31,230
You're the director of the Suzhou Branch

683
00:33:31,350 --> 00:33:32,790
of the Political Security Bureau

684
00:33:32,790 --> 00:33:34,750
of the Wang Regime.

685
00:33:35,790 --> 00:33:37,150
Do you know

686
00:33:37,710 --> 00:33:39,440
the former name of this prison?

687
00:33:41,270 --> 00:33:42,470
The local people

688
00:33:42,990 --> 00:33:45,310
called it Shizikou Prison.

689
00:33:47,030 --> 00:33:48,550
It's been here for hundreds of years.

690
00:33:48,550 --> 00:33:49,950
Shizikou means

691
00:33:50,260 --> 00:33:51,910
the lion's mouth.

692
00:33:52,150 --> 00:33:54,310
Once you're in it, there's no way you can get out.

693
00:33:54,310 --> 00:33:54,870
How is it?

694
00:33:55,030 --> 00:33:56,750
The court date is tomorrow.

695
00:33:57,750 --> 00:33:59,670
I heard that your wife hired

696
00:33:59,670 --> 00:34:01,600
a top lawyer for you from Shanghai.

697
00:34:03,550 --> 00:34:05,750
It's about our Gu family's reputation.

698
00:34:07,190 --> 00:34:07,690
Yes.

699
00:34:08,230 --> 00:34:09,150
A lawsuit

700
00:34:09,510 --> 00:34:12,219
is to clear the name as a traitor.

701
00:34:12,350 --> 00:34:13,150
I understand.

702
00:34:13,150 --> 00:34:14,750
I'm not a traitor, after all.

703
00:34:15,750 --> 00:34:16,429
Enter.

704
00:34:17,219 --> 00:34:18,280
You taught me that.

705
00:34:19,300 --> 00:34:20,600
I worked in No. 90

706
00:34:20,790 --> 00:34:22,310
for another purpose.

707
00:34:23,389 --> 00:34:24,230
Yes.

708
00:34:24,630 --> 00:34:27,070
Everyone in No. 90 knows that

709
00:34:27,830 --> 00:34:29,360
you're a spy planted

710
00:34:29,469 --> 00:34:31,440
in No. 90 by the New Fourth Army.

711
00:34:31,550 --> 00:34:33,909
You have witnesses and physical evidence, right?

712
00:34:33,909 --> 00:34:35,110
But do you know

713
00:34:35,670 --> 00:34:37,469
what the Supreme Court relies on

714
00:34:38,150 --> 00:34:40,190
to prove that you are

715
00:34:40,190 --> 00:34:41,719
an underground operative?

716
00:34:41,830 --> 00:34:43,550
Not based on witnesses or evidence,

717
00:34:43,550 --> 00:34:46,139
but entirely up to the testimonial from the NBIS.

718
00:34:46,139 --> 00:34:47,590
You need Mr. Dai himself

719
00:34:47,610 --> 00:34:49,320
to sign it.

720
00:34:49,429 --> 00:34:50,230
Do you have it?

721
00:34:50,230 --> 00:34:50,889
I guess not.

722
00:34:53,150 --> 00:34:55,230
I, Zhou Youren,

723
00:34:55,590 --> 00:34:56,230
have it.

724
00:34:57,310 --> 00:34:59,310
I am a real underground operative.

725
00:35:02,990 --> 00:35:03,650
Shameless!

726
00:35:05,510 --> 00:35:08,070
I'm not here to quarrel with you.

727
00:35:11,350 --> 00:35:12,440
Yizhong,

728
00:35:15,910 --> 00:35:18,170
let me tell you a piece of the latest news.

729
00:35:18,950 --> 00:35:21,390
Mr. Dai's latest instruction is

730
00:35:22,430 --> 00:35:25,750
that the purge of traitors this time focuses only on the positions,

731
00:35:25,750 --> 00:35:26,870
not the crime.

732
00:35:27,190 --> 00:35:29,470
So, we're pursuing accountability

733
00:35:29,830 --> 00:35:30,830
from the top down.

734
00:35:31,550 --> 00:35:32,390
For example,

735
00:35:33,070 --> 00:35:35,870
A governor-level official is sentenced to death.

736
00:35:37,310 --> 00:35:39,150
A minister, life sentence.

737
00:35:39,430 --> 00:35:41,270
An undersecretary, seven to ten years in prison.

738
00:35:41,270 --> 00:35:43,950
A chief of a bureau, three to five years.

739
00:35:44,910 --> 00:35:45,670
So,

740
00:35:45,940 --> 00:35:47,790
as your crime is simple,

741
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:51,020
I guess you'll only be sentenced to three years.

742
00:35:51,510 --> 00:35:53,110
If you have a good attitude,

743
00:35:53,630 --> 00:35:56,030
I'll plead with the judge.

744
00:35:56,590 --> 00:35:57,990
After you're convicted,

745
00:35:58,310 --> 00:35:59,310
I can get you out of there

746
00:35:59,310 --> 00:36:00,390
after a year or so.

747
00:36:01,510 --> 00:36:02,070
How is it?

748
00:36:03,150 --> 00:36:04,070
You said so much

749
00:36:04,790 --> 00:36:06,910
just because you don't want me to expose

750
00:36:06,910 --> 00:36:09,110
your atrocious crimes in court, right?

751
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:09,950
Look.

752
00:36:10,470 --> 00:36:12,510
We're talking about your business.

753
00:36:12,510 --> 00:36:14,370
Why do you have to get me involved?

754
00:36:14,510 --> 00:36:16,230
Are you going to testify against me

755
00:36:16,230 --> 00:36:17,290
in court tomorrow?

756
00:36:17,350 --> 00:36:18,030
Why?

757
00:36:19,110 --> 00:36:20,310
Do you have evidence?

758
00:36:22,910 --> 00:36:23,910
What do you think?

759
00:36:25,150 --> 00:36:26,550
Let's help each other.

760
00:36:28,310 --> 00:36:29,230
Cut the crap.

761
00:36:29,590 --> 00:36:30,750
Your crimes

762
00:36:31,710 --> 00:36:34,570
are serious enough for you to be sentenced to death.

763
00:36:34,630 --> 00:36:35,710
See you in court.

764
00:36:47,190 --> 00:36:49,550
The case regarding Gu Yizhong, the former director of the Suzhou Branch

765
00:36:49,550 --> 00:36:52,580
of the Political Security Bureau of the Wang Regime,

766
00:36:53,150 --> 00:36:55,070
who is suspected of treason,

767
00:36:55,590 --> 00:36:57,810
is now being publicly heard

768
00:36:58,630 --> 00:37:00,630
Bring in the defendant, Gu Yizhong.

769
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:15,670
Name.

770
00:37:17,710 --> 00:37:18,480
Gu Yizhong.

771
00:37:18,950 --> 00:37:19,710
Age.

772
00:37:20,870 --> 00:37:21,630
29.

773
00:37:22,110 --> 00:37:22,830
Hometown.

774
00:37:23,990 --> 00:37:25,030
Suzhou, Jiangsu.

775
00:37:25,470 --> 00:37:26,590
Your position at the time of your arrest.

776
00:37:26,590 --> 00:37:29,630
The director of the Suzhou Branch of the Political Security Bureau.

777
00:37:29,630 --> 00:37:31,550
What was your occupation

778
00:37:31,740 --> 00:37:33,070
before working for the Wang Regime?

779
00:37:33,070 --> 00:37:35,510
An architect specializing in historic buildings at Yizhong Architecture Research Society.

780
00:37:35,510 --> 00:37:37,110
Any other political status?

781
00:37:38,590 --> 00:37:39,150
No.

782
00:37:39,350 --> 00:37:41,550
You've never been a member of any party,

783
00:37:41,670 --> 00:37:43,280
including the Communist Party?

784
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:44,190
Tell the truth.

785
00:37:46,590 --> 00:37:47,190
No.

786
00:37:48,910 --> 00:37:50,870
But I've participated in the Communist Party's operation

787
00:37:50,870 --> 00:37:52,630
as an active applicant.

788
00:37:53,390 --> 00:37:54,630
Also, I've been working for the New Fourth Army.

789
00:37:54,630 --> 00:37:55,310
Stop.

790
00:37:56,150 --> 00:37:57,950
The court asked you

791
00:37:58,070 --> 00:38:01,070
how you joined the Wang Regime's intelligence agency

792
00:38:01,150 --> 00:38:02,700
and your experience there.

793
00:38:03,070 --> 00:38:04,710
And I've been working for the New Fourth Army

794
00:38:04,710 --> 00:38:06,430
and serving the anti-Japanese cause.

795
00:38:06,430 --> 00:38:09,220
On October 12, 1941,

796
00:38:10,190 --> 00:38:12,230
I accidentally participated in

797
00:38:12,790 --> 00:38:14,430
an operation of the anti-Japanese underground organization

798
00:38:14,430 --> 00:38:16,290
because of my friend Xiao Junxia.

799
00:38:16,320 --> 00:38:19,550
[Jiangsu High Court]

800
00:38:31,510 --> 00:38:33,790
Is that all you have to say?

801
00:38:36,150 --> 00:38:36,950
That's right.

802
00:38:37,600 --> 00:38:39,260
Anything else you want to add?

803
00:38:40,150 --> 00:38:41,210
Not for the moment.

804
00:38:42,070 --> 00:38:44,130
Bring in the prosecution's witness.

805
00:38:55,910 --> 00:38:56,590
Name.

806
00:38:56,750 --> 00:38:57,590
Zhou Youren.

807
00:38:57,830 --> 00:38:58,750
Position.

808
00:38:59,230 --> 00:39:02,030
Chairman of the Suzhou Traitor-purging Committee

809
00:39:02,030 --> 00:39:03,350
of the National Government。

810
00:39:03,350 --> 00:39:06,610
Suzhou Commissioner of the Military Statistical Bureau.

811
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:17,540
After our investigation,

812
00:39:17,990 --> 00:39:19,790
the evidence we found

813
00:39:19,870 --> 00:39:22,150
from No. 90 Agent Station

814
00:39:22,390 --> 00:39:24,350
shows Mr. Gu Yizhong

815
00:39:24,830 --> 00:39:27,190
even went as far as killing his father

816
00:39:27,210 --> 00:39:29,020
to earn the trust of

817
00:39:29,110 --> 00:39:30,910
Kondo Masao,

818
00:39:31,270 --> 00:39:33,780
the Japanese advisor at No. 90.

819
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:37,220
Everyone in Suzhou

820
00:39:37,360 --> 00:39:38,780
knew about it at the time.

821
00:39:38,720 --> 00:39:39,870
[Arresting the CPC member, Lu Junnuo]

822
00:39:39,110 --> 00:39:40,910
Gu Yizhong's father, Gu Xixing,

823
00:39:40,990 --> 00:39:42,910
was a senior member of the Kuomintang.

824
00:39:42,910 --> 00:39:44,950
He was also a famous general in the Northern Expedition.

825
00:39:44,950 --> 00:39:48,230
He had contributed a lot to the Kuomingtang State.

826
00:39:48,710 --> 00:39:50,270
Back then, he retired

827
00:39:50,470 --> 00:39:52,110
and returned to live in Suzhou.

828
00:39:52,110 --> 00:39:54,710
The Japanese invited Master Gu many times

829
00:39:54,710 --> 00:39:56,590
to become the magistrate of Wu County,

830
00:39:56,590 --> 00:39:59,710
but he'd rather die than obey.

831
00:40:00,430 --> 00:40:01,870
But he could never have expected

832
00:40:01,870 --> 00:40:04,680
that he'd be killed

833
00:40:04,910 --> 00:40:06,370
by his own son, Gu Yizhong.

834
00:40:07,190 --> 00:40:09,390
Both humans and gods were outraged by this matter.

835
00:40:09,390 --> 00:40:11,230
The law can't tolerate it.

836
00:40:20,390 --> 00:40:21,150
Gu Yizhong,

837
00:40:22,190 --> 00:40:23,790
how do you explain yourself?

838
00:40:27,230 --> 00:40:28,150
Gu Yizhong.

839
00:40:28,340 --> 00:40:29,200
Please answer.

840
00:40:38,830 --> 00:40:41,710
Among all Zhou Zhifei's accusations just now,

841
00:40:42,710 --> 00:40:44,070
only one thing was true.

842
00:40:44,830 --> 00:40:46,910
My father did die inside No. 90.

843
00:40:48,230 --> 00:40:49,270
Here's the thing.

844
00:40:51,390 --> 00:40:52,990
Zhou Zhifei and the Japanese

845
00:40:53,340 --> 00:40:54,510
took me and my father

846
00:40:54,510 --> 00:40:55,550
to No. 90.

847
00:40:57,150 --> 00:40:58,270
He threatened my father with my life

848
00:40:58,270 --> 00:41:00,930
and forced him to be the magistrate of Wu County.

849
00:41:01,630 --> 00:41:03,690
My father would rather die than obey.

850
00:41:03,860 --> 00:41:05,390
In order to save my life

851
00:41:05,950 --> 00:41:07,170
and protect the reputation of the Gu family,

852
00:41:07,170 --> 00:41:08,380
he shot himself

853
00:41:09,550 --> 00:41:10,670
in front of my eyes.

854
00:41:13,510 --> 00:41:15,390
I was the only one there.

855
00:41:16,830 --> 00:41:19,680
That is the truth.

856
00:41:20,310 --> 00:41:21,010
Your Honor,

857
00:41:22,310 --> 00:41:24,110
